<div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 columns text-center">
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Satisfy', cursive; text-align:center;">Welcome to Hangman!</h1>

        <br />
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="hoverable small-12 <%= current_game.present? && !current_game.finished? ? 'medium-6' : '' %> columns">
        <%= link_to new_game_path, :class => 'button expand hoverable' do %>
            <i class="fa fa-play"> New game</i>
        <% end %>
    </div>

    <% if current_game.present? && !current_game.finished? %>
        <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
            <%= link_to game_path, :class => 'button expand hoverable' do %>
                <i class="fa fa-refresh"> Continue game</i>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    <% end %>
    <br /><br /><br /><br />
    <div class="">
      <p style="font-family: 'Satisfy', cursive; text-align:left; font-size:34px;">"Hey Man, hit those 'buts', and see if you can find the right word.</p>
          <p style="font-family: 'Satisfy', cursive; text-align:right;font-size:34px;">Be careful though, if you fail to do so within the required attemps;
        You'll be Hang-Man."</p>
    </div>
</div>
